### Test Advanced Features - SMARTEK Platform
### Make sure backend is running on port 8083

### 1. Login as Learner to get JWT token
POST http://localhost:8081/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "Learner@smartek.com",
  "password": "Learner123"
}

### Save the token from response and use it below
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

###

### 2. Test Certification Templates Pagination
GET http://localhost:8083/api/certifications-badges/certification-templates/paginated?page=0&size=5&sortBy=id&sortDirection=DESC
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 3. Test Badge Templates Pagination
GET http://localhost:8083/api/certifications-badges/badge-templates/paginated?page=0&size=5&sortBy=id&sortDirection=DESC
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 4. Test Earned Certifications Pagination (replace {learnerId} with actual ID)
GET http://localhost:8083/api/certifications-badges/earned-certifications/learner/2/paginated?page=0&size=10&sortBy=issueDate&sortDirection=DESC
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 5. Test Earned Badges Pagination (replace {learnerId} with actual ID)
GET http://localhost:8083/api/certifications-badges/earned-badges/learner/2/paginated?page=0&size=10&sortBy=awardDate&sortDirection=DESC
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 6. Test Certificate Details Endpoint (replace {id} with actual certification ID)
GET http://localhost:8083/api/certifications-badges/earned-certifications/1/details
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 7. Test Different Page Sizes
GET http://localhost:8083/api/certifications-badges/certification-templates/paginated?page=0&size=25&sortBy=title&sortDirection=ASC
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 8. Test Page Navigation (page 1)
GET http://localhost:8083/api/certifications-badges/certification-templates/paginated?page=1&size=10&sortBy=id&sortDirection=DESC
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Expected Response Format:
# {
#   "content": [...],
#   "totalElements": 47,
#   "totalPages": 5,
#   "size": 10,
#   "number": 0,
#   "first": true,
#   "last": false,
#   "numberOfElements": 10,
#   "empty": false
# }
